Package model

Class Photo

java.lang.Object
model.Photo
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Photo class holds the path path of the photo as well as a list of tags associated with the photo.
